He can be heard on WKTU from 5 to 6 and also on had a mixshow "The Megamix" every Saturday night from 11-midnight on Sirius Satellite Radio The Beat channel 36.
After November 12, 2008, The Beat was replaced with BPM and is no longer on the channel.
He also produces a series of shows and events for New York City's reigning Dance music station WKTU, more recently KTU's Beatstock.
